Jack Finkelstein, Respondent, v. Yolande B. Finkelstein, Appellant.

No opinion. The order of this court, entitled John Anonymous v. Jane Anonymous, entered September 27, 1955, is vacated. Concur — Peck, P. J., Cohn, Breitel, Botein and Rabin, JJ. [See Anonymous v. Anonymous, ante, p. 961.]
